{
  "texts": [
    "These deviations and variations in responses underscore the dynamic nature of human-computer interactions and the complexities of maintaining strict adherence to a script.",
    "By addressing these challenges and enhancing adherence to the prompt script, PL environments can improve their effectiveness in delivering targeted instruction and fostering meaningful interactions between the tutor bot and students.",
    "The tutor bot proved to be an effective source of new information for the students.",
    "The data shows that the students gained new information from the tutor bot, and highlights the tutor bot's ability to deliver information and engage students in the learning process effectively.",
    "This helped the students write improved summaries of their education reforms."
  ]
}